<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.1.9">
<l>nontārāk kātaṉōy mellāvi yuḷḷulartta</l>
<l>nantā viḷakkamē nīyu maḷiyattāy</l>
<l>centā maraittaṭakkaṇ ceṅkaṉivā yemperumā</l>
<l>ṉantāmat taṇṭuḻā yācaiyāl vēvāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As the pain of painfully unsatiable love dries up inside [your] soft soul,</l>
<l>unwaxing lamp, you too are pitiable.</l>
<l>You burn from longing for the cool Tulsi from the pretty string of our</l>
<l>great lord with large red lotus eyes [and] a red fruit mouth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
